---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - CutGlueBuild.com" description="Learn how CutGlueBuild collects, uses, and protects your data.">
  <Header />

  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Last updated: June 23, 2025</p>

    <p class="mb-6">
      CutGlueBuild ("we", "us", or "our") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use,
      and safeguard your personal information when you use our platform.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      We collect information you provide directly (e.g., when you sign up, upload content, or contact us) and automatically
      (e.g., usage data, cookies, and analytics).
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Information</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      We use your information to operate and improve our services, provide customer support, personalize your experience,
      send updates, and ensure platform security.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">3. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      We do not sell your data. We may share data with trusted third-party service providers who assist us in operating our platform,
      subject to strict confidentiality agreements.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">4. Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      You can access, correct, or delete your personal data at any time. Contact us to make requests or if you have questions about your data.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">5. Security</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      We use modern security measures to protect your information, but no system is 100% secure. Use strong passwords and report any
      suspicious activity.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      We may update this Privacy Policy as needed. Weâ€™ll notify you of significant changes by posting a notice on our site or emailing you.
    </p>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
